#: plugin/woocommerce/settings/settings-tab.php:50
msgid "Breakdance WooCommerce Styles"
msgstr "أنماط البريك دانس ووكومرس"

#: plugin/woocommerce/settings/settings-tab.php:67
msgid "Breakdance's WooCommerce elements will not work correctly."
msgstr "لن تعمل عناصر WooCommerce الخاصة بـ Breakdance بشكل صحيح."

#: plugin/woocommerce/settings/settings-tab.php:71
msgid ""
"WooCommerce styles will come from the WooCommerce plugin's default "
"stylesheet, or your theme if you are using one that supports WooCommerce. "
"The styles can be created manually as well."
msgstr ""
"ستأتي أنماط WooCommerce من ورقة الأنماط الافتراضية لمكون WooCommerce "
"الإضافي، أو من القالب الخاص بك إذا كنت تستخدم واحدًا يدعم WooCommerce. يمكن "
"إنشاء الأنماط يدويًا أيضًا."

#: plugin/woocommerce/settings/settings-tab.php:87
msgid "The theme system is disabled. Breakdance will style WooCommerce."
msgstr "تم تعطيل نظام الموضوع. سوف Breakdance أسلوب WooCommerce."

#. translators: %1$s: theme name
#: plugin/woocommerce/settings/settings-tab.php:93
#, php-format
msgid ""
"You are using the \"%1$s\" theme with a child theme, Breakdance will style "
"WooCommerce."
msgstr ""
"أنت تستخدم السمة \"%1$s\" مع سمة فرعية، وسيقوم Breakdance بتصميم "
"WooCommerce."

#. translators: %1$s: theme name
#: plugin/woocommerce/settings/settings-tab.php:96
#, php-format
msgid "You are using the \"%1$s\" theme, Breakdance will style WooCommerce."
msgstr "أنت تستخدم السمة \"%1$s\"، وسيقوم Breakdance بتصميم WooCommerce."

#. translators: %1$s is the theme name
#: plugin/woocommerce/settings/settings-tab.php:104
#, php-format
msgid ""
"You are using the \"%1$s\" theme with a child theme which is recognized by "
"Breakdance. Breakdance has disabled its WooCommerce-specific CSS. However, "
"if the theme has made changes to WooCommerce's default HTML structure, some "
"of the Breakdance WooCommerce elements' styles and options may not work "
"correctly."
msgstr ""
"أنت تستخدم السمة \"%1$s\" مع سمة فرعية يتعرف عليها Breakdance. قام "
"Breakdance بتعطيل CSS الخاص بـ WooCommerce. ومع ذلك، إذا قام القالب بإجراء "
"تغييرات على بنية HTML الافتراضية لـ WooCommerce، فقد لا تعمل بعض أنماط "
"وخيارات عناصر Breakdance WooCommerce بشكل صحيح."

#. translators: %1$s is the theme name
#: plugin/woocommerce/settings/settings-tab.php:107
#, php-format
msgid ""
"You are using the \"%1$s\" theme which is recognized by Breakdance. "
"Breakdance has disabled its WooCommerce-specific CSS. However, if the theme "
"has made changes to WooCommerce's default HTML structure, some of the "
"Breakdance WooCommerce elements' styles and options may not work correctly."
msgstr ""
"أنت تستخدم السمة \"%1$s\" التي يتعرف عليها Breakdance. قام Breakdance بتعطيل"
" CSS الخاص بـ WooCommerce. ومع ذلك، إذا قام القالب بإجراء تغييرات على بنية "
"HTML الافتراضية لـ WooCommerce، فقد لا تعمل بعض أنماط وخيارات عناصر "
"Breakdance WooCommerce بشكل صحيح."

#. translators: %s is the theme name
#: plugin/woocommerce/settings/settings-tab.php:113
#, php-format
msgid ""
"The current theme \"%s\" isn't recognized. If your theme has WooCommerce "
"styles, they can interfere with the Breakdance WooCommerce styles and some "
"of the Breakdance WooCommerce elements' styles and options may not work "
"correctly."
msgstr ""
"لم يتم التعرف على السمة الحالية \"%s\". إذا كان القالب الخاص بك يحتوي على "
"أنماط WooCommerce، فمن الممكن أن تتداخل مع أنماط Breakdance WooCommerce وقد "
"لا تعمل بعض أنماط وخيارات عناصر Breakdance WooCommerce بشكل صحيح."

#: plugin/woocommerce/settings/settings-tab.php:118
msgid "Theme WooCommerce Styles"
msgstr "أنماط موضوع WooCommerce"

#. translators: %1$s is the element label, %2$s is the WooCommerce page label
#: plugin/woocommerce/utils.php:14
#, php-format
msgid ""
"The <b>\"%1$s\"</b> element can only be added to the <b>WooCommerce %2$s "
"Page</b>."
msgstr "لا يمكن إضافة عنصر<b>\"%1$s\"</b>إلا إلى صفحة<b>WooCommerce %2$s </b>."

#. translators: %s is the WooCommerce page label
#: plugin/woocommerce/utils.php:16
#, php-format
msgid ""
"Set the <b>WooCommerce %s Page</b> in the WP admin at <b>WooCommerce &gt; "
"Settings &gt; Advanced &gt; Page Setup</b>."
msgstr ""
"قم بتعيين صفحة<b>WooCommerce %s </b>في مسؤول WP "
"على<b>WooCommerce&gt;الإعدادات&gt;المتقدمة&gt;إعداد الصفحة</b>."

#. translators: %s is the WooCommerce page label
#: plugin/woocommerce/utils.php:20
#, php-format
msgid "No page has been set as the <b>WooCommerce %s Page</b>."
msgstr "لم يتم تعيين أي صفحة كصفحة<b>WooCommerce %s صفحة</b>."

#. translators: %1$s is the WooCommerce page label, %2$s is the page title,
#. %3$d is the page ID
#: plugin/woocommerce/utils.php:36
#, php-format
msgid ""
"The <b>WooCommerce %1$s Page</b> is currently set to <b>%2$s (ID: %3$d)</b>."
msgstr ""
"تم تعيين صفحة<b>WooCommerce %1$s </b>حاليًا على<b>%2$s (المعرف: %3$d)</b>."

